~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : wipe                                      ~FTRNUTS Version 3.0.2
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : wipe [<roomname>] <number of messages from top>/all

   This wipes the message board. If you give a number then it wipes that
   many messages from the top of the board where the oldest ones will be.
   If you specify "all" it wipes everything.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : read, write, search
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
